text: Constantly only getting part of my order and then when they "correct" it i get cold pizza or cold wings. Just today wasted my money on a pizza that was cold when it got here and my 3 year old grandson would not even eat. I was a regular customer and ussually tip well but i will no longer be due to this happening so often.
